TextArea Flags
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Gadget:	<TextArea>
#Line
#Wrap off
Bits:	0	- Gadget has vertical scrollbar.
	1 	- Gadget has a horizontal scrollbar.
	2  	- Gadget has word wrap.

Constants:
	<TextArea_Scrollbar_Vertical>
	<TextArea_Scrollbar_Horizontal>
#Line
To be used with <textarea_set_state>